entries.content: OpenAI icon updated: Split the logo into green outer ring (#10a37f) and white inner wave segments (#ffffff). Previously had black/transparent segments, now properly displays alternating green and white waves matching the official OpenAI branding.

Qwen icon updated: Added white fills (#ffffff) to all transparent areas (inner hexagonal pattern and center triangle). Purple gradient hexagonal frame remains, now with white sections filling the gaps for better visibility and contrast.
